description: How Many Will Share & Make A Stand Against Animal Cruelty?

  Without your support and voices, innocent life will continue to be victimized by cruelty and inhumanity - laws will continue to allow offenders to get away with their crimes with minimal punishment, the issues that animals endure and are subjected too on a daily basis will continue to increase, costing millions their well-being & their lives, and so much more...  This is a road we do not want to take!

   With your support and voices, you are not just helping our voiceless, you are speaking out with a powerful voice to make a difference in the world we live in, you are making a stand for a better and more compassionate future, and creating a road in which generations will travel and continue to build.

but such goals can only be accomplished if we take the first step and unite as one - for remaining in silence costs so much, and it is a price that innocent animals pay!

APRIL IS PREVENTION OF ANIMAL CRUELTY MONTH!  Let's Go Orange Together and Make A Difference!

Please Join Our #LetsGoOrange Campaign for Prevention of Animal Cruelty Month - Take a moment of your time to show your support ~ Our Facebook Page https://www.facebook.com/pages/Lets-Go-Orange/1064382010244996
